---
title: API Request Flow
---

@theme clean
@direction TB

#group Frontend
  Show Loading
  Render Results
  Display Error

#group API Gateway
  Validate Token
  Rate Limit Check
  Route Request

#group Backend
  Query Database
  Process Data
  Return Response

Show Loading -> Validate Token: "API call"
Validate Token -> Rate Limit Check
Rate Limit Check -> Route Request
Route Request -> Query Database
Query Database -> Process Data
Process Data -> Return Response
Return Response -> Render Results: "200 OK"
Rate Limit Check -> Display Error: "429"
